  55.  55     public function canonicalRedirection()
  56.  56     {
  57.  57         // Automatically redirect to the canonical URL if the current in is the right one
  58.  58         // $_SERVER['HTTP_HOST'] must be replaced by the real canonical domain
  59.  59         if (Validate::isLoadedObject($this->product) && strtoupper($_SERVER['REQUEST_METHOD']) == 'GET')
  60.  60         {
  61.  61             $canonicalURL = self::$link->getProductLink($this->product);
  62.  62             if (!preg_match('/^'.Tools::pRegexp($canonicalURL, '/').'([&?].*)?$/', Tools::getProtocol().$_SERVER['HTTP_HOST'].$_SERVER['REQUEST_URI']))
  63.  63             {
  64.  64                 header('HTTP/1.0 301 Moved');
  65.  65                 if (defined('_PS_MODE_DEV_') AND _PS_MODE_DEV_)
  66.  66                     die('[Debug] This page has moved<br />Please use the following URL instead: <a href="'.$canonicalURL.'">'.$canonicalURL.'</a>');
  67.  67                 Tools::redirectLink($canonicalURL);
  68.  68             }
  69.  69         }

  365. 365     public function pictureUpload(Product $product, Cart $cart)
  366. 366     {
  367. 367         if (!$fieldIds = $this->product->getCustomizationFieldIds())
  368. 368             return false;
  369. 369         $authorizedFileFields = array();
  370. 370         foreach ($fieldIds AS $fieldId)
  371. 371             if ($fieldId['type'] == _CUSTOMIZE_FILE_)
  372. 372                 $authorizedFileFields[(int)($fieldId['id_customization_field'])] = 'file'.(int)($fieldId['id_customization_field']);
  373. 373         $indexes = array_flip($authorizedFileFields);
  374. 374         foreach ($_FILES AS $fieldName => $file)
  375. 375             if (in_array($fieldName, $authorizedFileFields) AND isset($file['tmp_name']) AND !empty($file['tmp_name']))

  379. 379                     $this->errors[] = $error;

  383. 383                 /* Original file */

  386. 386                 /* A smaller one */
  387. 387                 elseif (!imageResize($tmpName, _PS_UPLOAD_DIR_.$fileName.'_small', (int)(Configuration::get('PS_PRODUCT_PICTURE_WIDTH')), (int)(Configuration::get('PS_PRODUCT_PICTURE_HEIGHT'))))
  388. 388                     $this->errors[] = Tools::displayError('An error occurred during the image upload.');
  389. 389                 elseif (!chmod(_PS_UPLOAD_DIR_.$fileName, 0777) OR !chmod(_PS_UPLOAD_DIR_.$fileName.'_small', 0777))
  390. 390                     $this->errors[] = Tools::displayError('An error occurred during the image upload.');
  391. 391                 else
  392. 392                     $cart->addPictureToProduct((int)($this->product->id), $indexes[$fieldName], $fileName);
  393. 393                 unlink($tmpName);
  394. 394             }
  395. 395         return true;

  430. 430     public function formatQuantityDiscounts($specificPrices, $price, $taxRate)
  431. 431     {
  432. 432         foreach ($specificPrices AS $key => &$row)
  433. 433         {
  434. 434             $row['quantity'] = &$row['from_quantity'];
  435. 435             // The price may be directly set
  436. 436             if ($row['price'] != 0)
  437. 437             {
  438. 438                 $cur_price = (Product::$_taxCalculationMethod == PS_TAX_EXC ? $row['price'] : $row['price'] * (1 + $taxRate / 100));
  439. 439                 if ($row['reduction_type'] == 'amount')
  440. 440                     $cur_price = Product::$_taxCalculationMethod == PS_TAX_INC ? $cur_price - $row['reduction'] : $cur_price - ($row['reduction'] / (1 + $taxRate / 100));
  441. 441                 else
  442. 442                     $cur_price = $cur_price * ( 1  - ($row['reduction']));
  443. 443                 $row['real_value'] = $price - $cur_price;
  444. 444             }
  445. 445             else
  446. 446             {
  447. 447                 global $cookie;
  448. 448                 $id_currency = (int)$cookie->id_currency;
  449. 449 
  450. 450                 if ($row['reduction_type'] == 'amount')
  451. 451                 {
  452. 452                     $reduction_amount = $row['reduction'];
  453. 453                     if (!$row['id_currency'])
  454. 454                         $reduction_amount = Tools::convertPrice($reduction_amount, $id_currency);
  455. 455 
  456. 456                     $row['real_value'] = Product::$_taxCalculationMethod == PS_TAX_INC ? $reduction_amount : $reduction_amount / (1 + $taxRate / 100);
  457. 457                 }
  458. 458                 else
  459. 459                 {
  460. 460                     $row['real_value'] = $row['reduction'] * 100;   
  461. 461                 }
  462. 462             }
  463. 463             $row['nextQuantity'] = (isset($specificPrices[$key + 1]) ? (int)($specificPrices[$key + 1]['from_quantity']) : -1);
  464. 464         }
  465. 465         return $specificPrices;
  466. 466     }
